name: Quick Draw (V)
Lore: 'It''s high noon on Dagobah, his droid''s reined in and Luke''s got a fistful of credits.',
Text: 'Unless Inner Strength on table, deploy on table.  Your lightsabers may target vehicles using 1 Force (each destiny draw is -2).  Once per turn, may lose 1 Force to deploy a character weapon (except a grenade) from Lost Pile.  Once per turn, may deploy [Virtual Block 1] Sai''torr Kal Fas from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)(Original concept by Lee Edwards - Florida State Winner 2004)(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
